<section id="contact">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-12 text-center">
                <h2 class="section-heading">About Us</h2>
                <h3 class="section-subheading text-muted">After the success of 2017, The Wellington Rowing Clubâ€™s very own Club Men are proud to announce the release of their 2018 calendar, which contains as much heart as it does cheek. Not only is this professional quality calendar guaranteed to put a smile the most sombre of faces, but it also provides you with the opportunity to get behind a fantastic cause. Like our rowing, we take the topic of mental health very seriously, particularly around mental health in male athletes like ourselves, a topic which is traditionally considered taboo amongst kiwi blokes. However, due to organisations such as The Mental Health Foundation of New Zealand getting the work done around raising awareness of mental health issues in kiwis, we are working toward a discrimination-free society we can all benefit from. 10% of all profit will be donated to this life-saving charity, which means you have a chance to make a difference. 
With orders being taken now, this not-so-serious calendar with a serious message will make the perfect Christmas gift for the person that has everything. All other proceeds will go towards supporting aspiring athletes, so troublemakers like us can stay on the water and off the streets, so be sure to share with friends, family, and anyone else that may be interested. 
                </h3>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-12">
                <form name="sentMessage" id="contactForm" novalidate>
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-lg-12 partition">

                            <div class="form-group">
                                <label class="section-subheading text-muted" for="calNum">Number of Calendars ($25ea) We will get in contact with you for payment details.</label>
                                <select class="form-control userInput" id="calNum">
                                    <option>1</option>
                                    <option>2</option>
                                    <option>3</option>
                                    <option>4</option>
                                    <option>5</option>
                                    <option>6</option>
                                    <option>7</option>
                                    <option>8</option>
                                    <option>9</option>
                                    <option>10</option>
                                </select>
                            </div>
                            <div class="form-group">
                                <label class="section-subheading text-muted" for="delOrPic">Delivery or Pickup (We will get in contact with you for convienient time.)</label>
                                <select class="form-control userInput" id="delOrPic">
                                    <option>Delivery</option>
                                    <option>Pick Up</option>                                
                                </select>
                            </div>
                            <input id="name" type="text" class="form-control userInput" placeholder="Your Name">
                            <input id="address" type="text" class="form-control userInput" placeholder="Your Address">
                             <label class="section-subheading text-muted" for="from">Please ensure your email is correct, we will use this as a primary means of contact.</label>
                            <input id="from" type="text" class="form-control userInput" placeholder="Your Email">                        
                            <input id="number" type="text" class="form-control userInput" placeholder="Contact Number" />
                            <button class="btn btn-default userInput" id="send_email">Send Email</button>
                            <h2 class="section-heading" id="message"></h2>
                        </div>
                        <script>
                            $(document).ready(function(){
                                var name,email,address,subject,text,number,calNum,plural;
                                $("#send_email").click(function(){
                                    name=$("#name").val();
                                    calNum=$("#calNum").val();
                                    address=$("#address").val();
                                    address = address.replace(/,/g, "|");
                                    email=$("#from").val();
                                    number=$("#number").val();
                                    delOrPic=$("#delOrPic").val();                                      

                                    plural = parseInt(calNum) < 2 ? " Calendar" : " Calendars";
                                    $("#message").text("Sending E-mail...Please wait");
                                    text = ("\n\nContact Email: " + email);
                                    text = (text + "\nContact Number: " + number);
                                    text = (text + "\nAddress: " + $("#address").val());

                                    subject = (name + ": " + calNum + plural);
                                    $.get("http://wrc-fundraiser.herokuapp.com/send",{subject:subject,text:text,name:name,calNum:calNum,
                                        address:address,email:email,number:number,delOrPic:delOrPic,plural:plural},function(data){
                                               /* $.get("http://localhost:8080/send",{subject:subject,text:text,name:name,calNum:calNum,
                                                    address:address,email:email,number:number,delOrPic:delOrPic,plural:plural},function(data){*/
                                                        if(data=="sent")
                                                        {
                                                            $("#message").empty().html("Email has been sent. We will get back to you as soon as we can!");
                                                        }
                                                        else{
                                                            $("#message").empty().html("Sorry! There was a problem in sending your email please try again.");
                                                        }
                                                    });

                                });
                            });
                        </script>
                    </div>
                </form>
